{"tid":141382,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"學神！3轉2會chok","createTime":"2017-03-03T01:18:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-04T15:40:33.000Z","uid":755,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f866497291d118b96cf4464dc30ffd225bfbd8ee","tid":141382,"uid":755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T01:18:12.000Z","msg":"如何解決求指點迷津<br />\n利申：就考"},{"pid":"a234f9e188b61e113d117545fc8a6981db021769","tid":141382,"uid":28800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T01:20:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"32826c29ea3266243cde6d07326ae4dbf1bbc433","tid":141382,"uid":22283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T01:22:04.000Z","msg":"轉得太急<br />\n要車速減慢<br />\n轉數細返<br />\n然後先落2"},{"pid":"025b50253e6a2e3e937a8b2ddc8281f1c6e10853","tid":141382,"uid":59882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T01:22:13.000Z","msg":"要夠慢先好轉<br />\n印慢落到十幾km 鬆brake 離合二波 吊極力子畀油"},{"pid":"2d9941ba06c65657fcc87228facc4042736b2cc1","tid":141382,"uid":46700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T01:24:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如何解決求指點迷津<br />\n利申：就考</blockquote><br />\n減慢啲先轉囉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n吊速<br />\n<br />\n你3轉2會因為太快而跳舞<br />\n你呢個時候就緊係有兩種做法啦<br />\n一係換2波吊速等你感覺到差唔多先完全放腳<br />\n或者入2波吊速加埋慢慢踏吓個剎車都會幫到你手<br />\n試幾次你就明<br />\n無論轉波入波你都係要吊一吊個離合<br />\n如果唔係跳住舞咁轉波真係人都死"},{"pid":"111ba8a34948242d078676b708a71151a64cab56","tid":141382,"uid":43331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T01:32:39.000Z","msg":"離合器放得慢啲<br />\n<br />\n利申 神之腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"840572905e7c894192cd3fc8b4f4c23ff1609fb7","tid":141382,"uid":57065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T01:39:25.000Z","msg":"先踩brake減速 直到feel到架車有少少對抗力就即刻鬆brake踩離合轉2波"},{"pid":"1bf5e1e75142fc37829a657aadbbe994960fe154","tid":141382,"uid":20602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T03:10:06.000Z","msg":"我之前3兆3咁, 第一個師傅冇教我, 肥左先知, 你要收到見到20KM/HR, 轉2波就唔CHOK<br />\n<br />\n不過極力子唔好放太快, 慢慢放"},{"pid":"2855cab130ea4f79d0aff70ff665c97e44c9adba","tid":141382,"uid":2764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T08:21:13.000Z","msg":"其實都係憑感覺<br />\n果時成日望住個咪錶去到20就轉波<br />\n後尾聽轉數聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0938a4999c2b4f8c9055b104e3b8f427ceafb963","tid":141382,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T08:21:45.000Z","msg":"左腳聽話D"},{"pid":"51f50fe94374e2d66eb53e277a5308f5d8bf5a22","tid":141382,"uid":51108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T08:29:54.000Z","msg":"落2波嗰陣，放clutch時hold住係個fiction point到直至match到轉數先放晒個clutch，咁就唔會chok"},{"pid":"1cc9d68f65bb0b94526294b872d45f1b9939621a","tid":141382,"uid":858,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T08:50:01.000Z","msg":"heel and toe就可以解決"},{"pid":"d999da2f3fc8afd470d14d8fceeda8c0078b0f5d","tid":141382,"uid":21861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T08:52:05.000Z","msg":"1）減速<br />\n2）轉二波<br />\n3）到磨擦點個陣吊一陣先放"},{"pid":"e8cdfaa3b3430fa7cc065df030e6b517e2e2e673","tid":141382,"uid":62355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T08:52:17.000Z","msg":"踩極力紙&gt;啪2波&gt;比空油&gt;放極力紙"},{"pid":"9b2219ee1b937176c082aa9b76df65bc9080e56c","tid":141382,"uid":68516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T08:54:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如何解決求指點迷津<br />\n利申：就考</blockquote><br />\n有兩個方法<br />\n1.到20km/h先轉二波<br />\n2.三轉二嗰陣補腳油(即係踭趾)"},{"pid":"29af69a531c63ef5f969282c19b96e44cff5a8e9","tid":141382,"uid":430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T09:03:52.000Z","msg":"踩clutch之後印幾下空油轉2波再慢慢鬆開clutch"},{"pid":"085627a5ec87ef28d48178db3745d16861523e1f","tid":141382,"uid":13543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T09:06:18.000Z","msg":"收慢D<br />\n轉波放腳前可以比D油"},{"pid":"cef51fd3d98b62055c8da70b8f2c31fbb4a4a810","tid":141382,"uid":858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T09:14:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如何解決求指點迷津<br />\n利申：就考</blockquote><br />\n有兩個方法<br />\n1.到20km/h先轉二波<br />\n2.三轉二嗰陣補腳油(即係踭趾)</blockquote><br />\n補腳油同heel toe兩回事喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27b2c4339d03ff696a4adac7ea892622b789c707","tid":141382,"uid":32060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T09:25:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如何解決求指點迷津<br />\n利申：就考</blockquote><br />\n有兩個方法<br />\n1.到20km/h先轉二波<br />\n2.三轉二嗰陣補腳油(即係踭趾)</blockquote><br />\n補腳油同heel toe兩回事喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔知heel toe比考牌官見到會唔會濕曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b4901721c38be808dd7a895cefd043e1cadc1ac","tid":141382,"uid":858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T09:28:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如何解決求指點迷津<br />\n利申：就考</blockquote><br />\n有兩個方法<br />\n1.到20km/h先轉二波<br />\n2.三轉二嗰陣補腳油(即係踭趾)</blockquote><br />\n補腳油同heel toe兩回事喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔知heel toe比考牌官見到會唔會濕曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n即pass<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f6853109cdbf